info: This corpus is an automatically annotated version of data from the Parallel Bible Corpus (Mayer & Cysouw 2014) that has been reduced in scope for the purposes of crosslinguistic research. Metadata from the original PBC file is included in this dict for reference, as well as the license information and the automatic POS annotations. The first three characters of the filename corresponds to the ISO 639-3 code for the respective language. The `tagged` key in this dict contains a list of lists, with the first item in each sublist being the verse number (following PBC convention) and the second being a list of tuples in [word, POS] format where `unk` represents unknown tags.

# notes:
#a Gaka sise da Bumbulvuŋ , asi naŋ mezleŋ , a wuɗ vu ngi sete .
#b Hunumaka Bumbulvuŋ ngi hunumo , asi a wuɗ vu ngi sete .
#c Hunumaka mijigin ngi Israyele , asi a wuɗ vu ngi sete .
#d Hunumaka migi duniya , asi a wuɗ vu ngi sete .
#e Hunumaka milaha Israyele , asi a wuɗ vu ngi sete .
#f hunumaka mukuso Israyeley mizliɗam hirnga , asi a wuɗ vu ngi sete .
#g Hunumaka mbur mindiraŋ walahay ati hay naŋ , asi a wuɗ vu ngi sete .
#h Hunumaka mbur mupus durum a hay Davit na , asi a wuɗ vu ngi sete .
#i Hunumaka mbur muwuna mangal ngi Sadok ngi gi mikuli na , asi a wuɗ vu ngi sete .
#j Hunumaka mbaray ngi Abrahama , asi a wuɗ vu ngi sete .
#k Hunumaka muwã ngi Izaka , asi a wuɗ vu ngi sete .
#l Hunumaka misi gidaŋ ngi Zakopo , asi a wuɗ vu ngi sete .
#m Hunumaka mbur muwuna Siyoŋ , asi a wuɗ vu ngi sete .
#n Hunumaka Buy madiɗa ngi buy madiɗahaya , asi a wuɗ vu ngi sete .
#o Dar a sa vula gidaŋ da mizli naŋhay amuŋ , ɓa mizli miteŋteŋ naŋhay gar , ziri mongoso ngi Israyeley ati mizli migweˀ ngi vaˀahay , a hunumakaŋ aseˀe . Haleluya .
